reg_info.act_under: County of Oxford Act   Loi sur le comté d’Oxford

content.content: 1. Ontario Regulation 949/93 made under the Regional Municipalities Act applies, with necessary modifications, to a by-law passed by the County Council under subsection 150 (1) of that Act by virtue of subsection 126 (7) of the County of Oxford Act. O. Reg. 951/93, s. 1.
